rows.label: tlk43400542_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Chairman Bahn over in Avaritia has
fallen from grace of late.

rows.label: tlk43400542_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Rumors of some dodgy backhand
dealings.

rows.label: tlk43400542_03_msg0004
rows.name:
They also say he managed to become
chairman via family connections...

rows.label: tlk43400542_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Bet he's managed to make a mint
on his dirty money...

rows.label: tlk43400542_03_msg0006
rows.name:
More than I could ever make working
in this place.
